reviews.review_text: Nice Jay Jay's studio is a wonderful place to make something better for us. Thank you. Neat story about the reels at the station. Good show to chill too.
Okay, wierd but true This US Blues Absolutely Rocks!
Pedal Steel Marvelous pedal steel action in this show. Jerry is one of the finest pedal steel players, only few are ahead of him, maybe Buddy Cage of the NRPS, that is about it. What a great sound
